  <brief_title>Vitamin D Levels and Postoperative Hypocalcemia After Total Thyroidectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Vitamin D Levels as a Prognostic Factor for Postoperative Hypocalcemia and Hypoparathyroidism After Total Thyroidectomy</official_title>
